	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator ca. 75-70. See MRR 2.493, but correct Verr. 2.1.26 to 2.1.126. On the relation of him and his family with the Lucilii Gamalae of Ostia, see M. Cebeillac, Akten des Vl. Internaz. Kongresses gr. U. lat. Epig. 457-462; MEFR 85, 1973, 517ff.\n" .
